artifacts.title: The <product> shall follow the Hilti standard Tool ID format, defined as:

<html:p dir="ltr" id="_1638551947935">The <product> shall follow the Hilti standard Tool ID format, defined as:</html:p>

<html:p dir="ltr" id="_1638551947938">• FFE (see HRID 330)</html:p>
<html:p dir="ltr" id="_1638551947939">• Version Information (see HRID 426)</html:p>
</html:div></ns0:primarytext>
